---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
import Sidebar from '../../components/Sidebar.astro';
const title = "Molecular Gas in HUDF - ArXiv Atlas";
---
<Base title={title}>
  <Sidebar />
  <main class="page-main">
    <div class="page-header">
      <h1>The ALMA Spectroscopic Survey: Molecular Gas Content of Galaxies at z=0.5-3</h1>
      <div class="page-meta">
        <span class="tag">arXiv:2603.09873</span>
        <span class="tag">2026-03-11</span>
        <span class="tag">astro-ph.GA</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="content">
      <h2 id="section-0">Overview</h2>
      <p>
        ALMA CO observations of 156 galaxies at z=0.5-3 in the Hubble Ultra Deep Field, measuring molecular gas content and star formation fueling.
      </p>

      <h2 id="section-1">Key Findings</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Molecular gas fraction</strong>: f_gas ∝ (1+z)^1.8, reaching ~50% at z~2</li>
        <li><strong>Depletion time</strong>: t_dep ~ 1 Gyr (constant with redshift)</li>
        <li><strong>Star formation efficiency</strong>: does not evolve strongly</li>
        <li>High-z SFRs driven by larger gas reservoirs, not enhanced efficiency</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 id="section-2">Relevance to Galaxy Evolution</h2>
      <p>
        Cosmic star formation history is driven by gas availability, not changing star formation physics. Gas accretion sustains high SFRs at early times.
      </p>

      <h2 id="section-3">Concepts</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><a href="/concepts/molecular-gas">Molecular gas</a></li>
        <li><a href="/concepts/gas-fraction">Gas fraction</a></li>
        <li><a href="/concepts/depletion-time">Depletion time</a></li>
        <li><a href="/concepts/star-formation-efficiency">Star formation efficiency</a></li>
      </ul>

      <div class="references">
        <h2 id="section-4">Citation</h2>
        <pre><code>@article&#123;decarli2026alma,&#125;
  title=&#123;ALMA Spectroscopic Survey in HUDF&#125;,
  author=&#123;Decarli, R. and others&#125;,
  journal=&#123;arXiv:2603.09873&#125;,
  year=&#123;2026&#125;
&#125;</code></pre>
      </div>

      <p><a href="https://arxiv.org/abs/2603.09873" target="_blank">View on arXiv →</a></p>
    </div>
  </main>
</Base>
